[0.000013, "o", " \u001b[33mв„№пёЏ Concept:\u001b[0m Crossplane v2 (HostCluster XR) + Cluster API (CAPI) + provider-KubeVirt (CAPK) declaratively turn a one-file request into a full Kubernetes cluster whose NODES are VMs.\r\n"]
[0.00004, "o", "\r\n"]
